# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Table 1: itertools.combinations_with_replacement class identity
#
# Wave 266 theme: itertools.combinations_with_replacement — C type identity.
#
# itertools.combinations_with_replacement.__class__.__name__ == 'type' (len 4)
# itertools.combinations_with_replacement.__name__ == 'combinations_with_replacement' (len 29)
# itertools.combinations_with_replacement.__module__ == 'itertools' (len 9)
# len(itertools.combinations_with_replacement.__mro__) == 2
#
# combinations_with_replacement is a C extension type in itertoolsmodule.c.
# It yields r-length subsequences with repeated elements allowed. New to extra138.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

