# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Table 3: itertools.batched class identity
#
# Wave 266 theme: itertools.batched — C type identity (Python 3.12+).
#
# itertools.batched.__class__.__name__ == 'type' (len 4)
# itertools.batched.__name__ == 'batched' (len 7)
# itertools.batched.__module__ == 'itertools' (len 9)
# len(itertools.batched.__mro__) == 2 — MRO is [batched, object]
#
# batched was added in Python 3.12. It yields successive fixed-length chunks
# from an iterable. It is a C extension type in itertoolsmodule.c. New to extra138.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

